  "descriptions": [
    {
      "text": "This game was in the final stages before release. At this vital time Kevin Costner's movie, Robin Hood: Prince of Thieves was released. But Arcadia didn't have the funds to obtain licensing from both Nintendo and the movie, so they were forced to pull out. The game itself is an action RPG and it shows the life of all the Merry-Men.",
